        <h3 class="collage__heading"><p>Start <strong>Your</strong> Subscription</p></h3>
        <div class="collage__description"><p>To <strong>get your first box for just $16</strong>, use code <strong>16KINDER</strong> at checkout.</p><p><br/></p><p>Looking for more savings? Click <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20221208115319/https://kinderbeauty.com/pages/subscription#select-a-plan" title="https://kinderbeauty.com/pages/subscription#select-a-plan">here</a> to view for additional subscription plans.</p></div>

