</div><div id="shopify-section-template--16128563380373__1663882585b79d1663" class="shopify-section"><div class="page-width">
    <h3 class="faqsection__heading">Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
    <div class="faq__section_faq__wrapp">
        
        <div class="accordion__wrapper">
            <h3 class="accordion__heading">
                <span>What is Kinder Beauty Box?</span>
                <div class="acordion__icon">
                    <span class="plus">
<svg width="14" height="14" viewbox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M6.24982 14V7.75H-0.000183105V6.25H6.24982V0H7.74982V6.25H13.9998V7.75H7.74982V14H6.24982Z" fill="#2B2424"/>
  </svg>
  </span>
                    <span class="minus">
<svg width="14" height="14" viewbox="0 0 14 2" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M6.31218 1.6875H0.583008V0.3125H6.31218H7.68718H13.4163V1.6875H7.68718H6.31218Z" fill="#2B2424"/>
  </svg>
  </span>
                </div>
            </h3>
            <div class="accordion__body"><p>Kinder Beauty Box is an activist-founded cruelty-free, vegan, and clean beauty box, on a mission to make the world a kinder place for animals, for people, and for the planet. Each monthly box is packed with at least $85 worth of hand-picked cosmetics, skincare, hair care products, accessories &amp; more!</p></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="accordion__wrapper">
            <h3 class="accordion__heading">
                <span>Are all products really vegan and cruelty-free?</span>
                <div class="acordion__icon">
                    <span class="plus">
<svg width="14" height="14" viewbox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M6.24982 14V7.75H-0.000183105V6.25H6.24982V0H7.74982V6.25H13.9998V7.75H7.74982V14H6.24982Z" fill="#2B2424"/>
  </svg>
  </span>
                    <span class="minus">
<svg width="14" height="14" viewbox="0 0 14 2" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M6.31218 1.6875H0.583008V0.3125H6.31218H7.68718H13.4163V1.6875H7.68718H6.31218Z" fill="#2B2424"/>
  </svg>
  </span>
                </div>
            </h3>
            <div class="accordion__body"><p>Absolutely, yes! Our three founders are all long-time vegan and animal activists, who personally ensure that each chosen product goes through a strict vetting process to guarantee that every product we send your way has not been tested on animals and doesn't contain any nasty animal ingredients or byproducts.</p></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="accordion__wrapper">
            <h3 class="accordion__heading">
                <span>I hate waste! What steps has Kinder Beauty taken to help protect the environment?</span>
                <div class="acordion__icon">
                    <span class="plus">
<svg width="14" height="14" viewbox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M6.24982 14V7.75H-0.000183105V6.25H6.24982V0H7.74982V6.25H13.9998V7.75H7.74982V14H6.24982Z" fill="#2B2424"/>
  </svg>
  </span>
                    <span class="minus">
<svg width="14" height="14" viewbox="0 0 14 2" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M6.31218 1.6875H0.583008V0.3125H6.31218H7.68718H13.4163V1.6875H7.68718H6.31218Z" fill="#2B2424"/>
  </svg>
  </span>
                </div>
            </h3>
            <div class="accordion__body"><p>We hate waste, too! That’s why we’ve taken earth-friendly steps we hope you’ll appreciate. For starters, our box is made from 100% recycled materials and is both biodegradable and compostable. The packing materials inside the box are also made from 100% recycled materials, and the ink used to print our logo and designs on the outside of the box, is an eco-friendly soy-based ink. Pretty cool, right?!<br/><br/>In terms of the individual product packaging, many of the brands we work with use only eco-friendly materials. However, not every brand is quite there yet. We hope consumers will join us in urging more brands to switch over to using only eco-friendly packaging.</p></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="accordion__wrapper">
            <h3 class="accordion__heading">
                <span>Did I hear that Kinder Beauty donates a portion of proceeds to charity each month?</span>
                <div class="acordion__icon">
                    <span class="plus">
<svg width="14" height="14" viewbox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M6.24982 14V7.75H-0.000183105V6.25H6.24982V0H7.74982V6.25H13.9998V7.75H7.74982V14H6.24982Z" fill="#2B2424"/>
  </svg>
  </span>
                    <span class="minus">
<svg width="14" height="14" viewbox="0 0 14 2" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M6.31218 1.6875H0.583008V0.3125H6.31218H7.68718H13.4163V1.6875H7.68718H6.31218Z" fill="#2B2424"/>
  </svg>
  </span>
                </div>
            </h3>
            <div class="accordion__body"><p>Yes! Every month a portion of proceeds goes to various animal rights and environmental causes. Kinder Beauty has supported organizations such as ASPCA, Farm Sanctuary, Los Angeles County Animal Care Foundation, Catskills Animal Sanctuary, and Compassion Over Killing, to name just a few.</p></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="accordion__wrapper">
            <h3 class="accordion__heading">
                <span>How does a Kinder Beauty subscription work?</span>
                <div class="acordion__icon">
                    <span class="plus">
<svg width="14" height="14" viewbox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M6.24982 14V7.75H-0.000183105V6.25H6.24982V0H7.74982V6.25H13.9998V7.75H7.74982V14H6.24982Z" fill="#2B2424"/>
  </svg>
  </span>
                    <span class="minus">
<svg width="14" height="14" viewbox="0 0 14 2" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M6.31218 1.6875H0.583008V0.3125H6.31218H7.68718H13.4163V1.6875H7.68718H6.31218Z" fill="#2B2424"/>
  </svg>
  </span>
                </div>
            </h3>
            <div class="accordion__body"><p>Choose any of our subscription plans (Monthly, 6-Month, or 12-Month) and your first monthly box will ship within 7-10 days. Each month we’ll start billing you* for your monthly shipments on the 8th of each month and ship your package out of our warehouse between the 9th and the 15th of the month. You’ll receive a shipping confirmation email once your box leaves the warehouse.<br/><br/><em>*If you are signed up for a 6-Month or 12-Month planned, you'll only be billed again at the end of your term.</em></p></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="accordion__wrapper">
            <h3 class="accordion__heading">
                <span>How much does Kinder Beauty cost?</span>
                <div class="acordion__icon">
                    <span class="plus">
<svg width="14" height="14" viewbox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M6.24982 14V7.75H-0.000183105V6.25H6.24982V0H7.74982V6.25H13.9998V7.75H7.74982V14H6.24982Z" fill="#2B2424"/>
  </svg>
  </span>
                    <span class="minus">
<svg width="14" height="14" viewbox="0 0 14 2" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M6.31218 1.6875H0.583008V0.3125H6.31218H7.68718H13.4163V1.6875H7.68718H6.31218Z" fill="#2B2424"/>
  </svg>
  </span>
                </div>
            </h3>
            <div class="accordion__body"><p>Our Monthly subscription plan costs just $26 per month.</p><p>If you commit to a 6-Month ($138) or 12-Month ($276) plan, you pay upfront, but the “per box” rate is discounted to $23/box.</p><p>Shipping is free for US customers. For international customers, there is an additional $9.99 per box fee for shipping and handling.</p></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="accordion__wrapper">
            <h3 class="accordion__heading">
                <span>When will I be billed for Kinder Beauty?</span>
                <div class="acordion__icon">
                    <span class="plus">
<svg width="14" height="14" viewbox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M6.24982 14V7.75H-0.000183105V6.25H6.24982V0H7.74982V6.25H13.9998V7.75H7.74982V14H6.24982Z" fill="#2B2424"/>
  </svg>
  </span>
                    <span class="minus">
<svg width="14" height="14" viewbox="0 0 14 2" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M6.31218 1.6875H0.583008V0.3125H6.31218H7.68718H13.4163V1.6875H7.68718H6.31218Z" fill="#2B2424"/>
  </svg>
  </span>
                </div>
            </h3>
            <div class="accordion__body"><p>You’ll be billed on the day you first sign up for KBB – and then on the 8th of the month, every month thereafter.</p></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="accordion__wrapper">
            <h3 class="accordion__heading">
                <span>What payment methods do you accept?</span>
                <div class="acordion__icon">
                    <span class="plus">
<svg width="14" height="14" viewbox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M6.24982 14V7.75H-0.000183105V6.25H6.24982V0H7.74982V6.25H13.9998V7.75H7.74982V14H6.24982Z" fill="#2B2424"/>
  </svg>
  </span>
                    <span class="minus">
<svg width="14" height="14" viewbox="0 0 14 2" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M6.31218 1.6875H0.583008V0.3125H6.31218H7.68718H13.4163V1.6875H7.68718H6.31218Z" fill="#2B2424"/>
  </svg>
  </span>
                </div>
            </h3>
            <div class="accordion__body"><p>For Subscription purchases, we currently accept Visa, Mastercard, American Express, Discover, and PayPal.</p><p>For Marketplace purchases, we currently accept Visa, Mastercard, American Express, Discover, PayPal, ShopPay, Google Pay, and Facebook Pay.</p></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="accordion__wrapper">
            <h3 class="accordion__heading">
                <span>Is it easy to cancel my subscription?</span>
                <div class="acordion__icon">
                    <span class="plus">
<svg width="14" height="14" viewbox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M6.24982 14V7.75H-0.000183105V6.25H6.24982V0H7.74982V6.25H13.9998V7.75H7.74982V14H6.24982Z" fill="#2B2424"/>
  </svg>
  </span>
                    <span class="minus">
<svg width="14" height="14" viewbox="0 0 14 2" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M6.31218 1.6875H0.583008V0.3125H6.31218H7.68718H13.4163V1.6875H7.68718H6.31218Z" fill="#2B2424"/>
  </svg>
  </span>
                </div>
            </h3>
            <div class="accordion__body"><p>It’s super easy, though we’ll hate to see you go! Your Kinder Beauty subscription can be canceled by logging into your account and going to the subscription tab under your name. There will be an option under Action that will allow you to cancel your subscription.</p><p>That’s it! No need to call or e-mail anyone, once you cancel your subscription you won’t be billed again. Though you will still receive any monthly Beauty boxes for which you’ve already paid.</p><p>If you’re having trouble doing so, please write in to our Customer Support (support@kinderbeauty.com) team before the 8th of the month to avoid auto-renewal.</p><p>However, our Marketplace orders get processed right away -- so if you need to cancel, please write in within an hour from the time you have placed your order.</p></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="accordion__wrapper">
            <h3 class="accordion__heading">
                <span>Can I sign up for just one box?</span>
                <div class="acordion__icon">
                    <span class="plus">
<svg width="14" height="14" viewbox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M6.24982 14V7.75H-0.000183105V6.25H6.24982V0H7.74982V6.25H13.9998V7.75H7.74982V14H6.24982Z" fill="#2B2424"/>
  </svg>
  </span>
                    <span class="minus">
<svg width="14" height="14" viewbox="0 0 14 2" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M6.31218 1.6875H0.583008V0.3125H6.31218H7.68718H13.4163V1.6875H7.68718H6.31218Z" fill="#2B2424"/>
  </svg>
  </span>
                </div>
            </h3>
            <div class="accordion__body"><p>Unfortunately, we do not currently have an option to buy just one box in our subscription offerings. However, we do occasionally offer past boxes for purchase in our Marketplace which is a great way to test the waters and see how great our boxes are! They are limited and always go fast so make sure you’re signed up for our emails so you know as soon as we add past boxes to the Marketplace!</p></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="accordion__wrapper">
            <h3 class="accordion__heading">
                <span>Can I purchase Kinder Beauty products without a subscription?</span>
                <div class="acordion__icon">
                    <span class="plus">
<svg width="14" height="14" viewbox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M6.24982 14V7.75H-0.000183105V6.25H6.24982V0H7.74982V6.25H13.9998V7.75H7.74982V14H6.24982Z" fill="#2B2424"/>
  </svg>
  </span>
                    <span class="minus">
<svg width="14" height="14" viewbox="0 0 14 2" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M6.31218 1.6875H0.583008V0.3125H6.31218H7.68718H13.4163V1.6875H7.68718H6.31218Z" fill="#2B2424"/>
  </svg>
  </span>
                </div>
            </h3>
            <div class="accordion__body"><p>Yes, you can! We have a Marketplace that's open to members and non-members where you can purchase individual items. Products range from items that have been features in our boxes, special bundles, and the occasional recent monthly box—all at Kinder prices. We add new "drops" in the Marketplace regularly, but the fan favorites always go fast, so make sure you sign up for our email list so you never miss a drop!</p></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="accordion__wrapper">
            <h3 class="accordion__heading">
                <span>When will you ship my first order?</span>
                <div class="acordion__icon">
                    <span class="plus">
<svg width="14" height="14" viewbox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M6.24982 14V7.75H-0.000183105V6.25H6.24982V0H7.74982V6.25H13.9998V7.75H7.74982V14H6.24982Z" fill="#2B2424"/>
  </svg>
  </span>
                    <span class="minus">
<svg width="14" height="14" viewbox="0 0 14 2" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M6.31218 1.6875H0.583008V0.3125H6.31218H7.68718H13.4163V1.6875H7.68718H6.31218Z" fill="#2B2424"/>
  </svg>
  </span>
                </div>
            </h3>
            <div class="accordion__body"><p>Your first monthly box will ship within 7-10 days. You’ll receive an email confirmation with tracking info as soon as your order ships.</p><p>If you've purchased from our Marketplace, those orders ship within a few days of your purchase.</p></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="accordion__wrapper">
            <h3 class="accordion__heading">
                <span>What are my gifting options?</span>
                <div class="acordion__icon">
                    <span class="plus">
<svg width="14" height="14" viewbox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M6.24982 14V7.75H-0.000183105V6.25H6.24982V0H7.74982V6.25H13.9998V7.75H7.74982V14H6.24982Z" fill="#2B2424"/>
  </svg>
  </span>
                    <span class="minus">
<svg width="14" height="14" viewbox="0 0 14 2" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M6.31218 1.6875H0.583008V0.3125H6.31218H7.68718H13.4163V1.6875H7.68718H6.31218Z" fill="#2B2424"/>
  </svg>
  </span>
                </div>
            </h3>
